style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要贏，香港人星期日一定要出嚟，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊記目標只有一個：撤回惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家copy呢個post喺Facebook, IG, Whatsapp share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組幫手整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ecce817358db0a768ede8d8f304fad0facbea9","tid":1224192,"uid":6571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散<br />\n釋放義士<br />\n清算黑警</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c1c94a8be8e2f7d1199d21ff01e88e096c6f9ed","tid":1224192,"uid":111578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2bd1c790213e296ca96984f6e9e3359ff617a8a7","tid":1224192,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>場仗未完，不撤不散！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>反送中懶人包（幫手一齊宣傳）</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1222056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1222056</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>民陣反送中遊行</strong></span></span><br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園（有可能再加入其他起點同時前進，請留意民陣fb最新消息）<br />\n遊行終點：政府總部<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民陣三罷反送中集會</strong></span></span><br />\n日期：6月17日（星期一）<br />\n集會地點：金鐘立法會外<br />\n當日行動：三罷（罷工罷市罷課）<br />\n（暫未有時間，要留意民陣fb最新安排